notes:
The Main Modifications include:  
• The plan period be extended to 2034/35 to ensure at least a 15-year plan period on adoption;  
• To apply the standard method for Local Housing Need so that the objectively assessed need for housing is at least 240 DPA.

Local Plan review to be completed within 6 months of PLan adoption (see Policy SP01b).  
Stepped approach to housing delivery: 
2011-16 additional homes 1555 (311 hpa); 
2016-21 additional homes 3000 (600 hpa); 
2021-26 additional homes 6000 (1200 hpa); 
2026-31 additional homes 6585 (1317 hpa).
